latestIgtvVideos.title: i cleaaned my teef w/ @vineeshas_dental_clinic
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hey everyone, sooo I went to do a full scaling, deep cleaning and polishing of my teeth sometime back and I feel ✨ frresshhh ✨
Vineesha’s Dental Clinic offers a variety of oral health services and is very clean and safe. Vineesha was very comfortable to talk to and is clearly good at what she does too :)
The cleaning and polishing made such a difference to me; I had slightly sensitive teeth for the next couple days and they’re back to normal now. I also did the Invisalign consultation and I am honestly so fascinated by it. If you’re looking for an alternative to metal braces, Invisalign teeth aligners have great reviews; more efficient, precise, quicker. It is more expensive though.

PSA: Take great care of your oral health, I cannot stress on how important it is. Teeth brushing twice a day at least, flossing and mouthwash, regular dentist visits 💯

#sponsoredvisit @themadrasdigital

latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Adith and I planned to do this video some 3 years back and it never happened. After that, we found ourselves in different parts of the world and now that we were in the same city for a bit, we thought — why not 🙆🏻‍♀️
So here’s a simple, fun video that will hopefully put a smile on your face :)

PS. Jiving is so tricky and this was my first time actually learning/doing it; thankfully Adith also happens to be a very patient teacher 🤗

Thank you, @prasanna1293 for helping us out at the last minute! :)

Drop a like and comment, and please do share 💕

latestIgtvVideos.title: Impromptu - This City by @samfischer
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I spent quite some time trying to ‘dance pretty’ and was so conscious of how my movement looked rather than how it felt. That’s not why I love dance, that’s not where I find my release, that’s not the way it used to be. So, I’m now taking small, steady steps back to what I love most — dancing with abandon. I’m still struggling with it but here’s a tiny attempt, I’ve got a loooong way to go.
